Package com.zeitheron.hammercore.api.crafting

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IBaseIngredient
    A base class for any ingredient.
    ICustomIngredient<T>
    A custom implementation that allows to get copies and origins of contained object.
    IFluidIngredient<T extends IFluidIngredient>  
    IGeneralRecipe
    A base interface for generic recipes.
    IItemIngredient<T extends IItemIngredient>
    An item implementation of IBaseIngredient that allows for items to be taken from IInventory
    INumericalIngredient<T extends java.lang.Number>
    A number tree ingredient implementation of IBaseIngredient.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GeneralRecipeRegistry<T extends IGeneralRecipe>
    A general registry for any subtype of IGeneralRecipe
    IngredientStack<T extends IBaseIngredient>
    The stack implementation for IBaseIngredient as delegate.
